# Complexity Comparison

## Brute Force

### Time Complexity

In the worst case, many branching choices are explored.

```
Exponential (worst case)
```

### Space Complexity

Recursive depth is at most 26 (letters in the alphabet).

```
O(26) ≈ O(1)
```

---

## Optimal

### Time Complexity

* Single traversal of the string: **O(n)**
* Each character update is **O(1)**

Total:

```
O(n)
```

### Space Complexity

* `best` array of size 26

Total:

```
O(26)

≈ O(1)
```

This satisfies the expected complexities of **O(n)** time and **O(1)** auxiliary space.
